description.en: Rapture was created by a small handful of developers that shared a vision –  that the blockchain could be utilized for true good. It is a blockchain cryptocurrency project that focuses on charitable giving. It was developed to reflect and promote the values of grace, hope, faith, and service. We are using the latest blockchain technology in a very real and practical way, and in doing so are providing benefit to those in need, and providing a new opportunity for people to achieve financial independence.
